  "description": "<h1>Kristiansand</h1>\n<h3>KRS · 1.0.0</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Subway-Builder-Modded/registry/refs/heads/main/maps/kristiansand-no/gallery/screenshot1.webp\" alt=\"Map Preview\"></p>\n<h2>Coverage</h2>\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Bounding box</strong></td><td>6.49642, 57.95848, 9.08523, 58.63676</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Playable Area</strong></td><td>11409 km²</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Population Summary</h2>\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Total Modeled Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">183,459</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Modeled Normal Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">161,059</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Modeled Special Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">22,400</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Map Statistics</h2>\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Demand Points</strong></td><td align=\"right\">6806</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Populations</strong></td><td align=\"right\">12,405</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Special Demand</h2>\n<details>\n<summary>Airports — 1125</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;KRS&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;1125&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Universities — 14,800</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;University of Agder Kristiansand&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;10,600&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;University of Agder Grimstad&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;3400&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Noroff Kristiansand&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;800&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Entertainment — 6215</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Lindesnes Fyr&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;275&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Kristiansand Dyrepark&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;2700&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Kristiansand Cannon Museum&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;70&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Kristiansand Domkirke&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;425&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Kilden Teater og Konserthus&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;550&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Aquarama&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;950&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Ravnedalen Scene&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;55&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Kristiansand Museum&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;110&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Kunstsilo&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;3935&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Natural History Museum and Botanical Garden University of Agder&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;150&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Sør Arena&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;425&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Kristiansand Stadion&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;80&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Military Bases — 260</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Luftforsvarets Skolesenter Kjevik&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;200&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Skjold&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;60&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n<br>\n\n<h2>Additional Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Building Collision</strong> — A buildings index is included, providing in-game collision geometry for all non-filtered buildings.</li>\n<li><strong>Neighborhood Labels</strong> — The map includes municipal and neighborhood labels derived from administrative boundary data.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Methodology</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Processed 250m x 250m country data for the bounding box.</li>\n<li>Applied a modified version of Colin&#39;s gravity model to generate commutes.</li>\n<li>Special demand added using the Demand Adder.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Data Sources</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://kartkatalog.geonorge.no/Metadata/bedrifter-pa-rutenett/7dcf4a32-b150-48f6-bae6-f8a25fab300c\">Statistisk sentralbyrå Bedrifter 250m 2026</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://kartkatalog.geonorge.no/Metadata/0c0ad0ce-55e8-4d73-9c12-0eb0e2454acb\">Statistisk sentralbyrå Befolkning 250m 2026</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>License</h2>\n<p>This map data is released under the <a href=\"https://github.com/rslurry/subwaybuilder-maps/blob/main/LICENSE\">GNU General Public License v3.0</a>.</p>\n<h2>Credits</h2>\n<p>Map authored by slurry</p>",
